108
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:26,800
Does this make sense to you?

109
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:28,840
The kitchen assistant.

110
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:32,180
The pick-up helper is Seo-woo's mom?

111
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,930
