now?

125
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:30,070
I'm sorry.

126
00:12:34,410 --> 00:12:36,410
At first, I was flustered,

127
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:40,040
so I couldn't tell you.

128
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:43,710
But you can't be the only one
who doesn't know.

129
00:12:45,210 --> 00:12:46,300
Min-jeong.

130
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,470
Believe it or not,

131
00:12:50,970 --> 00:12:52,140
it's true.

132
00:12:58,810 --> 00:13:00,520
MISAENG

