149
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,780
Hyeon-jeong.

150
00:13:54,490 --> 00:13:55,530
Hyeon-jeong.

151
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:01,290
Hyeon-jeong!

152
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:02,460
Yes. What?

153
00:14:03,250 --> 00:14:04,920
How spicy do you want that to be?

154
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,750
