because of her.

160
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:29,020
I'm just worried about her,
and I feel bad for her.

161
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:30,900
That's all.

162
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:33,240
Yu-ri is Seo-woo's mom,

163
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:36,370
