but it's complicated.

164
00:14:37,370 --> 00:14:39,410
That's why I keep sighing.

165
00:14:39,990 --> 00:14:42,040
Gang-hwa and you feel the same way, too.

166
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:44,670
I understand

167
00:14:46,330 --> 00:14:47,960
why Yu-ri hid from us

168
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,710
instead of coming to us first.

169
00:14:53,050 --> 00:14:54,090
Why?

170
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:56,640
Everyone is having a hard time
because I came back.

171
00:14:56,720 --> 00:15:00,220
Because of me, Gang-hwa and you
are such in pain.

172
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,850
